Hirunika Premachandra's protest march. Organized by the Samagi Vanitha Balakaya (SJB womens' wing), this march was a long trek from Point Pedro to 'Gnanakka' 's residence in Anuradhapura. Gnanakka aka Gnana Meniyo is a soothsayer turned businesswoman and political advisor (https://www.dailymirror.lk/recomended-news/Anuradhapura-Gnana-Akka-RENOWNED-SOOTHSAYER-S-HOTEL-COMES-UNDER-SPOTLIGHT/277-234007). This includes to Mahinda Rajapaksa, where she seems to have incredible levels of access (to mediate between him and Shavendra Silva, for example) https://english.theleader.lk/news/1240-46-slpp-mps-urge-premier-mahinda-rajapaksa-to-take-action-against-wimal
